{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c922df6d93","title":"关于下连队调查极为有用给林彪的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ef97d36544","index":0,"year":1961,"month":5,"day":7,"articleId":"c922df6d93"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"2cafae2591","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c922df6d93","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李井泉，当时任中共中央西南局第一书记、四川省委第一书记。"},{"id":"029022c28a","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c922df6d93","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指李井泉1961年5月8日关于粮食问题给毛泽东的信。信中说，关于粮食问题，我在南充、内江两地同干部、社员谈话和座谈时，听到的反映都比较强烈，主要是感到口粮标准低，要求增加口粮；按高级社时的分配办法，实行粮食三定；口粮按人口分配后，多余的粮食按劳动工分分配；及早宣布、固定国家征购任务。在我省两年来粮食比较困难的情况下，这个要求的出现是很自然的，也是合理的，这需要在小春分配中解决，以利于大春生产，争取今年的粮食丰收。我们对于粮食分配的原则是：大队统一掌握粮食，各级共同负责保管，按低标准供应，分期分批到户，超产队适当增加口粮，奖励粮按照工分分配。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7d5592cfca","type":"title","text":"转发李井泉\"关于粮食问题来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c922df6d93"},{"id":"2cafae2591","type":"paragraph","text":"李井泉同志此信，发给各中央局，各省、市、区党委，供","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c922df6d93"},{"id":"029022c28a","type":"subtitle","text":"参考。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c922df6d93"},{"id":"c50aeaef9a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c922df6d93"},{"id":"036200399a","type":"paragraph","text":"1961年5月9日上午2时，于上海。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c922df6d93"}],"page":{"id":"7a869751d9","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"c922df6d93","start":271,"end":271}}}},"__N_SSG":true}